00:36:28.520 --> 00:36:30.900 align:middle line:84%
If I've contributed to the
conversation about love

00:36:30.900 --> 00:36:33.590 align:middle line:84%
in some way, I feel
I'm on purpose.

00:36:33.590 --> 00:36:36.850 align:middle line:84%
So hopefully that's what's
happened with "Lovability."

